{"tid":2168926,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"患亞氏保加症 掟汽油彈少年感化三年","createTime":"2020-08-22T06:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T06:28:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23065c30de06d6a24b38e13e6bfd05206aefbe2e","tid":2168926,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/OUYMCLLVDVFDDMP4P3XAWDT6ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FOUYMCLLVDVFDDMP4P3XAWDT6ME%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=ee72f3ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FOUYMCLLVDVFDDMP4P3XAWDT6ME%2F&h=d013da76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/OUYMCLLVDVFDDMP4P3XAWDT6ME/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n患亞氏保加症 掟汽油彈少年感化三年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kR86yDWuaBJ8JgOHqQ_qHso_sEg=/1600x762/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ZNGCBWRABBMTAYYW7Q7RL6P3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkR86yDWuaBJ8JgOHqQ_qHso_sEg%3D%2F1600x762%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ZNGCBWRABBMTAYYW7Q7RL6P3I.jpg&h=77be1b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年9月柴灣已婚警察宿舍曾被市民包圍，警員到場驅散。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月抗爭者死守理大校園期間，患有亞氏保加症的16歲男生向柴灣已婚警察宿舍掟汽油彈，遭目擊事件的途人制服。男生早前在少年法庭承認罔顧生命受危害而縱火罪，昨接受判刑。裁判官何俊堯指，被告犯案是受亞氏保加症影響，加上年輕和有悔意，與一般情況有別，判刑不能只着重懲罰和阻嚇性，決定以感化令作判，但考慮控罪的嚴重性，判以最長的三年感化期，並需同時守宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官指犯案受病症影響<br />\n<br />\n何官指，案件對事主身心造成的損害屬較輕類別，財物損壞程度亦不高，罪責屬中等，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何官又指，案發於民居，有可能危及整楝大廈，加上被告夥同另一人犯案，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告與一名女子去年11月18日向柴灣已婚警察宿舍掟汽油彈，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC700006/19"},{"pid":"c2d6be1a971ae17a3d36114d32508810d794e04d","tid":2168926,"uid":370165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足take care"},{"pid":"8cbee0c747204fc71ef8da12db93c6b1f49cc5e7","tid":2168926,"uid":356218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}